        android:text="In the grades box you enter you grade, and in the Percentage boxes you enter the weight of you grade. If you have 10 Home Works and their percentage is 30%, don't put 30% 10 times, but average out your grades before you input them "
        android:textSize="11sp"
        android:layout_marginTop="60dp"/>

